dct_title_s: Map showing route of the electric telegraph from Suakin to Ra-Sai reduced from the map, by the late Captn. L. Rokeby, R.M.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, spot heights, and text. General road to Suakin and sections of telegraph are shown. Includes information on soil quality, vegetation, fauna, and groundwater. Locations, dates of, and distances from Suakin to expedition encampments are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 44 (1874), pp. 152-63; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 44 1874
